Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.03,0:01:00.58,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(800,0)}強くなれる理由を知った
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.58,0:01:08.75,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}僕を連れて　進め
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:16.89,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}泥だらけの走馬灯に酔う
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.34,0:01:21.60,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}強張る心　震える手は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.60,0:01:23.98,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}掴みたいものがある
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.98,0:01:25.77,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それだけさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.77,0:01:29.36,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}夜の匂いに(I’ll spend all thirty nights)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.36,0:01:32.90,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}空睨んでも (Staring into the sky)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.90,0:01:38.07,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}変わっていけるのは　自分自身だけ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.07,0:01:40.07,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それだけさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.07,0:01:46.83,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}強くなれる理由を知った
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.83,0:01:53.21,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}僕を連れて　進め
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.21,0:01:58.05,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}どうしたって消せない夢も　止まれない今も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.05,0:02:02.35,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰かのために強くなれるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.35,0:02:07.39,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何度でも立ち上がれ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.39,0:02:12.07,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}世界に打ちのめされて　守る意味を知った
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.07,0:02:16.61,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}紅蓮の華よ　咲き誇れ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.61,0:02:21.91,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}運命を照らして
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.61,0:02:21.91,op-cn,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.03,0:01:00.58,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(800,0)}知曉了為何能變強
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.58,0:01:08.75,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}與我攜手 前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:16.89,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沉醉於遍佈泥土的走馬燈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.34,0:01:21.60,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}頑固的心 顫抖的手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.60,0:01:23.98,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為有想緊握之物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.98,0:01:25.77,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.77,0:01:29.36,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在夜的氣息中{\fnA-OTF Ryumin Pr5 B-KL\fs40\fsp0}(I’ll spend all thirty nights)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.36,0:01:32.90,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}久久凝視天空{\fnA-OTF Ryumin Pr5 B-KL\fs40\fsp0}(Staring into the sky)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.90,0:01:38.07,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能夠改變的 卻只有自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.07,0:01:40.07,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.07,0:01:46.83,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知曉了為何能變強
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.83,0:01:53.21,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}與我攜手 前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.21,0:01:58.05,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}揮之不去的夢境 無法阻擋的現實
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.05,0:02:02.35,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要能為那個人而變強
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.35,0:02:07.39,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不論多少次 都要重新振作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.39,0:02:12.07,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}被世界摧毀 知曉了守護之意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.07,0:02:16.61,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}紅蓮之花 驕傲綻放
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.61,0:02:21.91,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}將命運照亮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.87,0:02:23.87,op-cn,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.00,0:21:19.54,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(691,300)}悲しみに囚われたくはない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.54,0:21:28.89,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}俯いた場所に涙を落として行きたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.89,0:21:32.14,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}運命を振りほどいて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.14,0:21:38.10,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}走り出せるはずなんだ　願いは叶うはずなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.10,0:21:41.48,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,0)}叩き潰せ　昨日の葛藤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.48,0:21:46.78,ed-jp,,0,0,5,,{\blur2}cry for the future from the edge of darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.78,0:21:53.29,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}向かい風を乗っ取って　嵐の先は見えなくたって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.29,0:21:58.21,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}もう道は選べない　勝ち残れ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.21,0:22:06.05,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}迷いはいつも愛情と怒りを秤にかける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.05,0:22:13.10,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(0,500)}さあ　立ち上がるんだ　もう一度
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.60,0:22:27.07,ed-jp,,0,0,3,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}今　君はその刃を　どこへ振り下ろす？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.02,0:00:00.02,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.00,0:21:19.54,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(691,300)}不願在悲傷之中迷失
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.54,0:21:28.89,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}不願在倒下之處落淚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.89,0:21:32.14,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}無視命中注定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.14,0:21:38.10,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}定能勇往直前 定能實現夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.10,0:21:41.48,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,0)}斬斷昨日糾葛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.48,0:21:46.78,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}cry for the future from the edge of darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.78,0:21:53.29,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}馭風而行 即便被風暴遮蔽前路
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.29,0:21:58.21,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也只能前進 戰勝強敵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.21,0:22:06.05,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}躊躇之時 總在愛恨間搖擺不定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.05,0:22:13.10,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(0,500)}再一次站起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.60,0:22:27.07,ed-cn,,0,0,3,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}此刻 你會將那刀刃 揮向何方？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.07,0:22:29.11,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.31,0:00:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,獸之呼吸 柒之型
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.81,0:00:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,空間識覺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.17,0:00:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.46,0:00:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了 在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,能感受到很強的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.01,0:00:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你真厲害 伊之助
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.39,0:00:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.51,0:00:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,要想繼續前進就必須先解決掉他們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.40,0:00:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,難道就沒有辦法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.37,0:02:29.00,biaoti,,0,0,0,,{\pos(904,386)\fad(981,0)}不讓自己 而讓別人站在前面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.01,0:02:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,禰 禰 禰豆…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,禰 豆 豆 豆… 豆子…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.91,0:03:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.57,0:03:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,麻煩死了 把他們都砍了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.45,0:03:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.12,0:03:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,一定會有辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.25,0:03:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 不能傷害他們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.13,0:03:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,村田
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡交給我 你們繼續前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你個被嚇尿的弱雞 說什麼大話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.47,0:03:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你才被嚇尿了 臭野豬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.60,0:03:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒跟你說話 給我閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.81,0:03:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然剛才我確實很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,但我也是鬼殺隊劍士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.40,0:03:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.53,0:03:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,現在也知道可以砍斷絲讓他們停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.36,0:03:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,這些被操縱的人動作很單純
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.03,0:03:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我也會小心蜘蛛的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.25,0:03:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,鬼的附近應該有更強的傀儡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.67,0:03:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你們兩個快去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.29,0:03:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.92,0:03:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我們走 伊之助
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.30,0:04:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你放手 我要先揍他一拳才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.93,0:04:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,誰是臭野豬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.51,0:04:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你煩不煩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,少廢話 快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.02,0:04:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,等我回來絕對要揍你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.69,0:04:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.07,0:04:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我絕對要揍他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.69,0:04:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,別說這種話了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他可是叫我臭野豬了 紋次郎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.20,0:04:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫炭治郎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.28,0:04:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,方向沒錯嗎 是這邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我的感覺不會有錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.83,0:04:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.04,0:04:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,這些煩人的絲是什麼鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.75,0:04:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,說明我們十分接近鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.76,0:04:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,又出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.22,0:04:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.52,0:04:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不要過來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:04:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,快帶階級更高的人過來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.57,0:05:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不然所有人都會被殺的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.74,0:05:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.45,0:05:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.33,0:05:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你們能打贏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.54,0:05:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,越接近我 絲就越粗 越有力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.63,0:05:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,人偶也會越強
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,媽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.52,0:05:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你能贏的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.77,0:05:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,累
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.52,0:05:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是有點慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.20,0:05:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是再不快點 我就去告訴爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.71,0:05:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,沒 沒問題 媽媽可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.79,0:06:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽一定會保護你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.59,0:06:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,所以不要告訴你爸 不要告訴他 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那你快點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.70,0:06:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,去死吧 去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.91,0:06:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,快點去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.16,0:06:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不然我要遭殃了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.13,0:06:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.71,0:06:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.05,0:06:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我被操縱了 行動和平時完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.55,0:06:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我們原本沒有這麼強的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.53,0:07:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,鬼在用絲強迫她行動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,就算骨頭斷了也不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.75,0:07:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好過分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.58,0:07:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,真難纏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.21,0:07:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,這聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.26,0:07:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,殺 殺了我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,手腳都斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,骨頭 骨頭扎到了內臟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.90,0:07:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,一動起來 就劇痛難忍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.03,0:07:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,反正都要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.95,0:07:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:08:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,給我個痛快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.25,0:08:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.29,0:08:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你等等 一定有辦法救他們的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.72,0:08:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.97,0:08:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的好煩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.80,0:08:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.35,0:08:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他自己都說要我們殺了他了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.06,0:08:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,他們的動作也很快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.81,0:08:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,要是再拖下去 我們會被幹掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.44,0:08:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.69,0:08:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我在想辦法 你等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不想用招式
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.03,0:08:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 絲被砍斷了很快又會連上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,要讓他們停下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.54,0:08:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.62,0:08:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.63,0:08:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好 跟上來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.96,0:08:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你小子 怎麼到處逃竄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.76,0:08:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.35,0:09:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,全集中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.32,0:09:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,力氣好大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.28,0:09:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好 順利掛上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.20,0:09:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼啊 我也想玩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.19,0:09:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,看到沒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.39,0:09:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你能做到的事我也能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.56,0:09:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 沒看到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.03,0:09:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.49,0:09:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒法分心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.37,0:10:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.70,0:10:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,都是些沒用的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,看來只能出動那個人偶了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,禰豆子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.27,0:10:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,禰豆子 你在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.65,0:10:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,禰豆子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,炭治郎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.11,0:10:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,野豬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.49,0:10:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啾太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.41,0:10:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你們在哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.38,0:10:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,啾太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你追過來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.34,0:11:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.10,0:11:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然沒有禰豆子可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.27,0:11:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我錯了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.10,0:11:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,來 我們一起去找禰豆子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.15,0:11:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.45,0:11:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,看到沒 我比你扔得更高
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.20,0:11:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 還剩一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.16,0:11:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好 我再來一次 你看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.79,0:11:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 這樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.66,0:11:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,總之你溫柔點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.54,0:11:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,脆弱的人類人偶 你們已經沒用了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.21,0:11:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,一群廢物 廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.98,0:11:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡 都被幹掉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.29,0:12:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.67,0:12:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.68,0:12:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊 很近了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.56,0:12:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,風向變了 我的鼻子也能派上用場了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.64,0:12:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣就能知道鬼的位置了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.11,0:12:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,還有兩個氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.94,0:12:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.61,0:12:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,伊之助
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.61,0:12:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是我先發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.95,0:12:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,看我不砍了他的頭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.37,0:12:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,0:12:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有頭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.55,0:13:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,禰豆子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.59,0:13:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.39,0:13:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你們去哪裡了啊 炭治郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,伊之助
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.94,0:13:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,別把我一個人丟在這麼可怕的森林裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.16,0:13:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.12,0:13:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺越來越氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.08,0:13:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,快點找到禰豆子 跟這可怕的森林說再見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.17,0:13:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,禰豆子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.06,0:13:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,這傢伙沒有要害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.90,0:14:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有頭要怎麼砍頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,伊之助
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,冷靜點 斜著肩砍下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,從脖子根部的右邊砍到左腰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.29,0:14:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,要砍的範圍很廣 而且看起來很硬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.33,0:14:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不過應該可以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.17,0:14:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 要一起上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.47,0:14:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但也不至於躲不開
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.64,0:14:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不好 有蜘蛛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.47,0:14:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,動不了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.64,0:14:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,要被幹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.66,0:14:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,伊之助
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.74,0:14:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我們一起戰鬥吧 一起思考吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.83,0:14:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我們齊心協力 來打倒這隻鬼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你小子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,別再讓我感覺暖暖的了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.67,0:15:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,別礙事 你閃開
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,伊之助 踩在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.99,0:15:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,伊之助 跳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.49,0:15:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,全集中 水之呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,肆之型
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.37,0:15:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,打潮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.46,0:15:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,斜著砍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.18,0:15:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡 好氣人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.89,0:15:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,全都和他想得一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.97,0:16:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都像理所當然一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.23,0:16:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,就像流淌的河水一樣自然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.32,0:16:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他不自己衝到前面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.11,0:16:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,而是在掌控整個戰局
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.64,0:16:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好 砍到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.10,0:16:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 我們贏了 伊之助
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,伊之助？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.24,0:16:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你能做到的事 我也能做到 白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.67,0:17:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,這氣味是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.38,0:17:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,原來是這樣啊 伊之助
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.34,0:17:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,被幹掉了 被幹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.68,0:17:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那個人偶是最快最強的了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.35,0:17:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,說起來 都怪累來威脅我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.64,0:17:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,害我著急了 一著急就…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,上面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,水之呼吸 壹之型
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.24,0:17:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,要被殺了 要被砍掉頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.41,0:17:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,快點 快想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.16,0:17:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.42,0:17:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,要是死掉 就能解脫了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.22,0:17:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,就能變輕鬆了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.22,0:18:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,伍之型
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.85,0:18:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,干天之慈雨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.74,0:18:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.11,0:18:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,就像被雨滴溫柔地拍打著一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.91,0:18:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,一點都不痛 一點都不痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.67,0:18:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,只有溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.50,0:18:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到居然能死得這麼安寧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.47,0:18:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣就能解脫了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.44,0:18:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.57,0:18:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 原諒我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你為什麼生氣啊 我怎麼惹你不高興了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.41,0:19:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,就因為你不知道他為什麼生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.38,0:19:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.96,0:19:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.17,0:19:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽又被爸爸罵了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.23,0:19:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,別這樣 不要 不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那眼神…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.67,0:19:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.38,0:19:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,還是人類的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.71,0:20:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好像有人用溫柔的眼神看過我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.43,0:20:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.69,0:20:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,想不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.36,0:20:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那個人一直都很關心我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.12,0:20:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那個人現在怎麼樣了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.13,0:20:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,有十二鬼月
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.47,0:20:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.06,0:20:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,小心一點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.02,0:21:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,有十二鬼月
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.19,0:21:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,真正的十二鬼月 就在這座山裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.46,0:22:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你能做到的事我也能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.09,0:22:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 我知道你做不到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.01,0:22:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.89,0:22:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你永遠記不住我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.72,0:22:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你的名字我當然記得住
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.68,0:22:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,造門炭子郎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.06,0:22:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不對哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.69,0:23:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,早門蛋五郎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.98,0:23:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.81,0:23:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,大門豚太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.98,0:23:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,完全不對
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.57,0:23:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 現在要開始大正傳聞悄悄話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.32,0:23:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,伊之助叫別人的名字 每七次就能叫對一次
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.24,0:23:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,都叫錯三次了 真的能叫對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.66,0:23:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,洞門干治郎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.91,0:23:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,接近了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.08,0:23:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,找門炭五郎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.29,0:23:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.08,0:23:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,鑿門千治郎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.29,0:23:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,差一點點了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.46,0:23:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,竈門…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.04,0:23:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,名字而已 無所謂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.59,0:23:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,差一點點就能聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.84,0:23:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,下集 第17集 將一件事做到最好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.26,0:23:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你是你 我是我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.55,0:23:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,懂了沒 炭治郎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.14,0:23:40.06,zhu,,0,0,0,,待續
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.02,0:23:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,
